  "detailed_description": "<h1>IMPORTANT AF</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681270/extras/8a08c3afd7a85632ef8f06f99c971a41.avif?t=1758217088\" width=600 height=184 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                  ROADMAP BELOW ⇓</p></p><br><h1>Future Roadmap</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681270/extras/c915685fee071944d9c8e4b251a50ce9.avif?t=1758217088\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681270/extras_big/c915685fee071944d9c8e4b251a50ce9.avif?t=1758217088 width=800 height=954 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681270/extras/360f4724180f8784fec6d2f25a5323af.avif?t=1758217088\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681270/extras/fce3793412f0b9a15aabcd114bc69f0a.avif?t=1758217088\" width=600 height=120 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681270/extras/1ddcb84c22533a86ce38b91921f51c30.poster.avif?t=1758217088\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681270/extras/1ddcb84c22533a86ce38b91921f51c30.webm?t=1758217088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681270/extras/1ddcb84c22533a86ce38b91921f51c30.mp4?t=1758217088\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>The Race against the clock in this retro-inspired arena shooter, where waves of demons and a ticking timer test your speed and precision. Master swift movement and weapons to climb the leaderboard and prove how far you can go.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681270/extras/bdee153c68c0852c2c2ec085fbb93608.avif?t=1758217088\" width=600 height=120 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681270/extras/6b3f1e0e1fe086a6898edac157b86470.poster.avif?t=1758217088\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681270/extras/6b3f1e0e1fe086a6898edac157b86470.webm?t=1758217088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681270/extras/6b3f1e0e1fe086a6898edac157b86470.mp4?t=1758217088\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on unique and bone-chilling monsters.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many Game Modes to choose from, all with their own leaderboards. and their own Difficulty Style</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Lore to keep you engage in theories (fr)</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kill Demons, Power up your Secondary Weapon and clear the arena in a style.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master different demons' patterns, Beat the timer of top players from the Leaderboard.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make your Own Art Style with in-game customizer</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump and Dash your way through the Arena.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Intense arena-based combat inspired by OGs like Devil Daggers & Hyper Demon</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Smooth Gameplay with fast movement.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No Micro Transactions or Paid DLCs.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681270/extras/2156d619709810280b960ae39acc4be7.poster.avif?t=1758217088\" width=800 height=800 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681270/extras/2156d619709810280b960ae39acc4be7.webm?t=1758217088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681270/extras/2156d619709810280b960ae39acc4be7.mp4?t=1758217088\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
