.webm?t=1758217088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681270/extras/6b3f1e0e1fe086a6898edac157b86470.mp4?t=1758217088\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on unique and bone-chilling monsters.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many Game Modes to choose from, all with their own leaderboards. and their own Difficulty Style</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Lore to keep you engage in theories (fr)</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kill Demons, Power up your Secondary Weapon and clear the arena in a style.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master different demons' patterns, Beat the timer of top players from the Leaderboard.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make your Own Art Style with in-game customizer</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump and Dash your way through the Arena.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Intense arena-based combat inspired by OGs like Devil Daggers & Hyper Demon</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Smooth Gameplay with fast movement.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No Micro Transactions or Paid DLCs.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681270/extras/2156d619709810280b960ae39acc4be7.poster.avif?t=1758217088\" width=800 height=800 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681270/extras/2156d619709810280b960ae39acc4be7.webm?t=1758217088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681270/extras/2156d619709810280b960ae39acc4be7.mp4?t=1758217088\" t